<i>Somebody bet on the bay</i>

1754
01:32:46,394 --> 01:32:48,191
<i>Watch old Bill in the first furlong</i>

1755
01:32:48,396 --> 01:32:50,387
- <i>Doo-dah, doo-dah</i>
- <i>Doo-dah, doo-dah</i>

1756
