<i>Bet him to win</i>
<i>And you can't go wrong</i>

1757
01:32:52,633 --> 01:32:54,692
- Amen.
- <i>Oh, doo-dah day</i>

1758
01:32:54,902 --> 01:32:56,961
<i>I'll bet my money</i>
<i>With dancing Dan</i>

1759
